column5: Hello  I got into a heated arguement about when Cameron lake is closed for the season,   my buddy was saying that the MNR opened up most Kawartha's lake to ice fish for panfish...  I told him they close close to the end of the month....  Can anyone here help clarify,  I dont have the regs and my laptop is too slow for a PDF file of them.....  Any help would be appreciated  Dave
Closed as of November 15th. New regs come into effect on Jan.1st for  FMZ17.
